list.abstract: 《Invisible》是由美国歌手Taylor Swift演唱的一首歌曲。由Taylor Swift、 Robert Eills Orrall作词作曲。收录于Taylor Swift2006年10月24日发行的专辑《Taylor Swift》中。
时隔 11 年，叶树茵终于要发新专辑了！距离上一张专辑 1994 年的“非常属于我”实在太久了，虽然她一直还有在唱，但大多数人其实并不知道，对他们来说，她或许是个仅仅存在于记忆之中的名字，也或许是场早就放弃的痴心等待，但是这个秋天突如其来地，我们终于又将可以听见叶子的声音……

yingyinNormal.en: Number one: The Invisible Hand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一章：看不见的手。

yingyinNormal.en: Plus, the world's always changing brightness and hotness, and there's invisible germs floating everywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有，世界里的亮度和温度不断改变，四处都漂着看不见的细菌。

yingyinNormal.en: I suppose you could say they're invisible, hidden in a dark room that's at the center of a maze that's located somewhere up here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 应该说它是看不见的，就藏在迷宫中央的小黑屋里而这个迷宫则藏在这里。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sure I'm invisible. Hi, Drax. Damn it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我坚信没人能看到我。德拉克斯。该死的。

yingyinNormal.en: She doesn't want much. She just wants to be invisible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她要的不多。她只想消失。

yingyinNormal.en: You going somewhere, Mr. Ross? Trying to be invisible?
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯先生，你要去哪儿？是想从这个课堂上消失吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't. But I would still like to be acknowledged. What? Just because I'm pregnant, I'm invisible. Definitely not invisible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，但我还是希望有被重视的感觉，我怀孕了就变成隐形人？你绝不是隐形人。

yingyinNormal.en: He aches for the spotlight. He feels almost invisible without it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他渴望聚光灯，没有聚光灯，他几乎感觉自己是隐形的。

yingyinNormal.en: Long range and untraceable, it would be invisible to Klingon sensors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 射程远，难以被发现，可以对克林贡帝国的传感器隐形。

yingyinNormal.en: That's your side and this is my side. Do not cross the invisible line.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那边是你的，而这一边是我的地盘。不许跨过这条隐形的界线。

yingyinNormal.en: It's something almost invisible tucked away inside the leaf of a plant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这项演变深藏于植物叶片之内并不易为人所知。

yingyinNormal.en: You just had to blindly play, searching around in rooms for an invisible dot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你只需要随便玩玩，在房间里找一个隐形的方块。

yingyinNormal.en: There's an invisible wall standing between us and them and nobody's doing anything about it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们与他们之间有道无形的墙，而大家都没在想办法解决。

yingyinNormal.en: And that gives us strength. That strength is a powerful thing. It's not invisible. It radiates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这给了我们力量，这股力量无比强大，不容忽视，光芒万丈。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, you don't have to stop, I'm invisible, I'm not here. But I don't... Who approved that order?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不必停下来，我是隐形人，我不在这儿。对，可是，我不…是谁批准这批货的？

yingyinNormal.en: Are you serious? I've mastered the ability of standing so incredibly still that I become invisible to the eye. Watch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不是吧？我已经掌握了纹丝不动站立的能力肉眼是看不到我的。看好了。

yingyinNormal.en: From that height it will be invisible! No one will have any idea! And what do I do when I get to the first cavaletti?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在那个高度看不见，没人会知道。走到第一个卡瓦拉帝时怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: Generally it sits on an invisible surface. You can see stuff sliding down the sides, and disappearing down the drain, as it were.
